data.description: Fantastic!  Super Clean, Super Nice, 3 Bed/ 1 Bath / Over 1700 SqFt open concept home.  This property is move in ready!  Recently remodeled in 2018 this home features original hardwood floors, new laminate flooring, new windows, new stucco, new roof, new plumbing and an updated electrical panel with all new receptacles.  The kitchen is very classy and modern with beautiful hickory cabinets and laminate flooring.   On the exterior you have easy to maintain xeriscaping with fresh rock in the front as well as in the back and includes a 6ft metal fence (back) with a parking area. This property is centrally located by some popular restaurants in town, as well as schools and other everyday amenities like the very nice & tranquil park across the street.  This is a great opportunity to own your own home or to use as an investment!  Don't miss out! Schedule your showing today.
